1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,008
Bugungi videoning mavzusi nima? Talabaning bir kuni. Yaxshi oʻqiyapmiz, baribir!

2
00:00:10,008 --> 00:00:13,008
1-Sahna: Ertalabki shoshilinchlik / Testga tayyorgarlik

3
00:00:13,008 --> 00:00:16,074
Xayrli tong!

4
00:00:16,097 --> 00:00:19,564
A, xayrli tong!

5
00:00:19,587 --> 00:00:22,853
Hozir soat necha?

6
00:00:22,876 --> 00:00:26,310
Yetti yarim.

7
00:00:26,333 --> 00:00:28,799
Voy, bu yomon!

8
00:00:28,822 --> 00:00:33,181
Bugun birinchi darsdan test bor.

9
00:00:33,205 --> 00:00:37,195
Rostdanmi?

10
00:00:37,219 --> 00:00:40,209
Shoshiling!

11
00:00:40,232 --> 00:00:45,750
Ha. Nonushta qilishga vaqtim yoʻq.

12
00:00:45,774 --> 00:00:50,367
Stolda non bor.

13
00:00:50,390 --> 00:00:52,823
Yeyapsizmi?

14
00:00:52,846 --> 00:00:55,632
Rahmat.

15
00:00:55,656 --> 00:00:58,369
Yeyishni boshlayman.

16
00:00:58,392 --> 00:01:01,726
Qahva ham ichasizmi?

17
00:01:01,749 --> 00:01:04,825
Men quyib beraman.

18
00:01:04,849 --> 00:01:11,982
Yoʻq, vaqt yoʻq, suv yetadi.

19
00:01:12,005 --> 00:01:14,238
Tushunarli.

20
00:01:14,261 --> 00:01:17,980
Test qiyinmi?

21
00:01:18,004 --> 00:01:23,037
Ha, juda qiyin boʻladi deb oʻylayman.

22
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:28,527
Kecha kechgacha koʻp oʻqidingizmi?

23
00:01:28,551 --> 00:01:34,122
Ha, kutubxonada oʻn ikkigacha oʻqidim.

24
00:01:34,146 --> 00:01:37,914
Bu juda zoʻr!

25
00:01:37,937 --> 00:01:41,404
Albatta, hammasi yaxshi boʻladi.

26
00:01:41,427 --> 00:01:44,160
Rahmat.

27
00:01:44,183 --> 00:01:46,816
Harakat qilaman.

28
00:01:46,839 --> 00:01:50,950
Tayyorgarlik tugadimi?

29
00:01:50,974 --> 00:01:56,007
Sumkamga hammasini solib qoʻydim.

30
00:01:56,030 --> 00:02:00,547
Endi ketamizmi?

31
00:02:00,571 --> 00:02:04,004
Ha, ketamiz.

32
00:02:04,027 --> 00:02:11,132
Bugungi videodagi mavzuni takrorlash uchun sayt havolasini tavsif va eng yuqori kommentda topishingiz mumkin. *Sayt oldindan ogohlantirmasdan oʻchirilishi mumkin.

33
00:02:11,132 --> 00:02:14,132
2-Sahna: Borish usullari va ob-havo

34
00:02:14,132 --> 00:02:18,276
Har kuni issiq ekan, shundaymi?

35
00:02:18,299 --> 00:02:21,933
Ha, shunday.

36
00:02:21,956 --> 00:02:26,901
Bugun maktabga qanday borasiz?

37
00:02:26,924 --> 00:02:30,991
Bugun avtobusda boraman.

38
00:02:31,014 --> 00:02:35,410
Men velosipedda boraman.

39
00:02:35,433 --> 00:02:41,138
Unda, avtobus bekatigacha birga boring.

40
00:02:41,162 --> 00:02:44,395
Ha, shunday qilamiz.

41
00:02:44,418 --> 00:02:50,485
Velosipedda maktabgacha necha daqiqa ketadi?

42
00:02:50,508 --> 00:02:56,208
Taxminan oʻn besh daqiqa.

43
00:02:56,231 --> 00:02:58,701
Tez ekan!

44
00:02:58,725 --> 00:03:02,825
Avtobus yigirma daqiqa ketadi.

45
00:03:02,848 --> 00:03:10,614
Lekin yomgʻirli kunlarda velosipedda borish qiyin, shuning uchun avtobusga oʻtiraman.

46
00:03:10,637 --> 00:03:14,510
Ha, shunday.

47
00:03:14,534 --> 00:03:20,034
Menga ham yangi velosiped kerak.

48
00:03:20,057 --> 00:03:24,894
Dam olish kunida birga koʻrishga boramizmi?

49
00:03:24,918 --> 00:03:27,551
Yaxshi boʻlardi.

50
00:03:27,574 --> 00:03:31,143
Dokon qayerda?

51
00:03:31,166 --> 00:03:36,866
Bekat oldida katta doʻkon bor.

52
00:03:36,889 --> 00:03:39,523
Qimmatmi?

53
00:03:39,546 --> 00:03:44,412
Yo'q, unchalik qimmat emas deb o'ylayman.

54
00:03:44,435 --> 00:03:49,634
A, u yerda avtobus bekatimi ekan.

55
00:03:49,658 --> 00:03:56,335
Ha. Men bu yerdan velosipedda boraman.

56
00:03:56,358 --> 00:03:59,149
Tushunarli.

57
00:03:59,172 --> 00:04:02,446
Ehtiyot bo'ling.

58
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:04,970
Rahmat.

59
00:04:04,993 --> 00:04:08,093
Keyinroq ko'rishamiz.

60
00:04:08,116 --> 00:04:11,116
3-Sahna: Salomlashish va unutilgan narsalar

61
00:04:11,116 --> 00:04:14,349
Xayrli tong!

62
00:04:14,372 --> 00:04:17,406
Xayrli tong!

63
00:04:17,429 --> 00:04:20,962
Bugun erta ekansiz-ku.

64
00:04:20,985 --> 00:04:26,018
Ha, biroz erta yetib keldim.

65
00:04:26,041 --> 00:04:30,075
O'qituvchi allaqachon keldi mi?

66
00:04:30,098 --> 00:04:34,836
Yo'q, hali sinfda yo'q.

67
00:04:34,859 --> 00:04:37,626
Shundaymi.

68
00:04:37,649 --> 00:04:42,682
A, mening o'chirgichim yo'q.

69
00:04:42,705 --> 00:04:46,972
Sumkangizda yo'qmi?

70
00:04:46,995 --> 00:04:50,661
Yo'q, yo'q.

71
00:04:50,684 --> 00:04:54,068
Uyni unutib qoldim.

72
00:04:54,092 --> 00:04:59,125
Mening o'chirgichimdan foydalaning.

73
00:04:59,148 --> 00:05:02,048
Rahmat.

74
00:05:02,071 --> 00:05:05,305
Katta yordam bo'ldi.

75
00:05:05,328 --> 00:05:09,311
Bugungi birinchi dars nima?

76
00:05:09,334 --> 00:05:13,400
Yapon tili grammatikasi.

77
00:05:13,423 --> 00:05:16,808
Uyga vazifani qildingizmi?

78
00:05:16,832 --> 00:05:22,698
Ha, kecha kechqurun hammasini bajardim.

79
00:05:22,721 --> 00:05:26,093
Men hali qilmadim.

80
00:05:26,117 --> 00:05:29,617
Uchta savol qolgan.

81
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:32,873
Qiyin edi-mi?

82
00:05:32,896 --> 00:05:37,730
Ha, juda qiyin edi.

83
00:05:37,753 --> 00:05:40,339
O'rgating, iltimos.

84
00:05:40,363 --> 00:05:43,065
Albatta.

85
00:05:43,088 --> 00:05:45,834
Qaysi masala?

86
00:05:45,857 --> 00:05:51,924
Ushbu sahifaning eng pastidagi masala.

87
00:05:51,947 --> 00:05:57,780
A, bu so'zni ishlatamiz.

88
00:05:57,803 --> 00:06:00,803
4-Sahna: Tushlik rejasi

89
00:06:00,803 --> 00:06:04,736
Allaqachon o'n ikki bo'ldi-ku.

90
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:06,659
Ha.

91
00:06:06,682 --> 00:06:10,673
Tushlik qilamizmi?

92
00:06:10,697 --> 00:06:13,534
Yaxshi boʻlardi.

93
00:06:13,557 --> 00:06:18,224
Bugun nima yeymiz?

94
00:06:18,247 --> 00:06:22,998
Oshxonada yeymizmi?

95
00:06:23,022 --> 00:06:26,815
Bugun tashqarida ovqatlanmoqchiman.

96
00:06:26,838 --> 00:06:33,173
Maktab oldidagi restoranga boramizmi?

97
00:06:33,196 --> 00:06:38,096
U yerda ovqatlar mazali-mi?

98
00:06:38,119 --> 00:06:40,819
Ha.

99
00:06:40,842 --> 00:06:44,075
Juda mazali.

100
00:06:44,098 --> 00:06:46,965
Qimmatmi?

101
00:06:46,988 --> 00:06:55,488
Yo'q, talabalar uchun tushlik besh yuz yendan, arzon.

102
00:06:55,511 --> 00:06:58,344
Bu yaxshi ekan.

103
00:06:58,367 --> 00:07:02,139
Nima tavsiya qilasiz?

104
00:07:02,163 --> 00:07:07,707
Menimcha, kare-rays eng mazali.

105
00:07:07,731 --> 00:07:12,081
Men ham kareyni yaxshi ko'raman.

106
00:07:12,104 --> 00:07:14,771
Shunday bo'lsin.

107
00:07:14,794 --> 00:07:20,146
Ko'p odam bor, shoshilaylik.

108
00:07:20,169 --> 00:07:22,719
Ha, shunday.

109
00:07:22,743 --> 00:07:26,244
Yuguraylikmi?

110
00:07:26,267 --> 00:07:31,300
Xavfli, piyoda boramiz.

111
00:07:31,323 --> 00:07:33,867
Tushunarli.

112
00:07:33,890 --> 00:07:39,003
O, doʻkon koʻrinib qoldi.

113
00:07:39,027 --> 00:07:42,293
Boʻsh joy bormi?

114
00:07:42,316 --> 00:07:44,686
Ha.

115
00:07:44,709 --> 00:07:49,099
Derazaga yaqin joy boʻsh.

116
00:07:49,122 --> 00:07:51,901
Yaxshi boʻldi-ku.

117
00:07:51,925 --> 00:07:55,025
Oʻtiramiz.

118
00:07:55,048 --> 00:07:58,048
5-Sahna: Kanji oʻqish va maʼnosini tushunish / Kanji qanday oʻqiladi va maʼnosi nima?

119
00:07:58,048 --> 00:08:03,039
Uzr, bir oz gaplashsam boʻladi-mi?

120
00:08:03,063 --> 00:08:07,363
Ha, nima deysiz?

121
00:08:07,386 --> 00:08:12,719
Bu kitobdagi kanjini oʻqiy olmayapman.

122
00:08:12,742 --> 00:08:15,621
Qayerda?

123
00:08:15,644 --> 00:08:18,878
Koʻrsating.

124
00:08:18,901 --> 00:08:23,867
Bu qizil yozuv joyida.

125
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:30,804
A, bu „toshokan“ deb oʻqiladi.

126
00:08:30,828 --> 00:08:34,863
„Toshokan“, shundaymi?

127
00:08:34,887 --> 00:08:38,246
Maʼnosi nima?

128
00:08:38,269 --> 00:08:43,027
Kitoblar koʻp boʻlgan joy.

129
00:08:43,050 --> 00:08:46,183
Tushunarli.

130
00:08:46,206 --> 00:08:49,506
Rahmat.

131
00:08:49,529 --> 00:08:53,763
Lugʻatingiz yoʻqmi?

132
00:08:53,786 --> 00:08:58,978
Ha, bugun olib kelmaganman.

133
00:08:59,002 --> 00:09:03,572
Mening lugʻatimni bersam boʻladi-mi?

134
00:09:03,595 --> 00:09:06,662
Rostdan ham boʻladi-mi?

135
00:09:06,685 --> 00:09:09,351
Rahmat.

136
00:09:09,374 --> 00:09:13,731
Ha, iltimos.

137
00:09:13,755 --> 00:09:17,752
Ertangi test uchun oʻqiyapsizmi?

138
00:09:17,776 --> 00:09:21,809
Ha, shunday.

139
00:09:21,832 --> 00:09:25,616
Yodlash kerak boʻlgan narsalar koʻp.

140
00:09:25,639 --> 00:09:31,988
Kanji testi har hafta boʻladi, qiyin-ku.

141
00:09:32,012 --> 00:09:39,193
Ha. Lekin asta-sekin yaxshilanayapman.

142
00:09:39,217 --> 00:09:42,567
Bu yaxshi yangilik-ku.

143
00:09:42,590 --> 00:09:47,770
Ha. Lugʻatni keyin qaytaraman.

144
00:09:47,794 --> 00:09:51,231
Shoshilmang.

145
00:09:51,255 --> 00:09:55,122
Qachon boʻlsa ham boʻladi.

146
00:09:55,145 --> 00:09:58,145
6-Sahna: Yarim kunlik ish haqida / Yarim kunlik ish haqida suhbat

147
00:09:58,145 --> 00:10:03,645
Bugungi darslar hammasi tugadi-ku.

148
00:10:03,668 --> 00:10:06,377
Charchadingizmi?

149
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:09,767
Juda charchadim.

150
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:12,490
Men ham.

151
00:10:12,513 --> 00:10:16,213
Endi nima qilamiz?

152
00:10:16,236 --> 00:10:20,303
Bugun yarim kunlik ishim bor.

153
00:10:20,326 --> 00:10:22,826
Shundaymi.

154
00:10:22,848 --> 00:10:27,158
Qayerda ishlaysiz?

155
00:10:27,182 --> 00:10:30,816
Vokzal yaqinidagi doʻkonda.

156
00:10:30,839 --> 00:10:34,339
Soat nechidan nechigacha?

157
00:10:34,362 --> 00:10:39,881
Kechqurun soat 5 dan kecha soat 9 gacha.

158
00:10:39,904 --> 00:10:42,737
Qiyin-ku.

159
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:47,227
Haftada necha marta ishlaysiz?

160
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:50,750
Haftada 3 marta.

161
00:10:50,773 --> 00:10:54,485
Pul koʻp olasizmi?

162
00:10:54,509 --> 00:10:58,776
Yoʻq, unchalik koʻp emas.

163
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:02,534
Lekin qiziqarli.

164
00:11:02,557 --> 00:11:06,746
Mijozlar bilan yapon tilida gaplashasizmi?

165
00:11:06,769 --> 00:11:08,836
Ha.

166
00:11:08,859 --> 00:11:11,725
Har kuni gaplashamiz.

167
00:11:11,748 --> 00:11:15,048
Yaxshi mashq boʻladi.

168
00:11:15,071 --> 00:11:19,138
Men ham yarim kunlik ish qilishni xohlayman.

169
00:11:19,161 --> 00:11:24,548
Unda, mening doʻkonimizning mudiri bilan gaplashaymi?

170
00:11:24,572 --> 00:11:27,038
Rostdanmi?

171
00:11:27,061 --> 00:11:29,660
Iltimos.

172
00:11:29,684 --> 00:11:31,917
Ha.

173
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:35,486
Endi ketishim kerak.

174
00:11:35,509 --> 00:11:38,009
Omadingizni sinab koʻring!

175
00:11:38,032 --> 00:11:40,499
Ertaga koʻrishamiz.

176
00:11:40,522 --> 00:11:43,422
Ertaga koʻrishamiz.

177
00:11:43,445 --> 00:11:46,383
Ehtiyot boʻling, uyga boring.

178
00:11:46,406 --> 00:11:49,406
7-Sahna: Xarid qilish va kechki ovqatni tayyorlash

179
00:11:49,406 --> 00:11:55,397
Bugungi kechki ovqatga nima pishiramiz?

180
00:11:55,421 --> 00:12:01,214
Goʻsht yeyishni xohlayman.

181
00:12:01,237 --> 00:12:07,471
Unda, supermarketga borib xarid qilaylik.

182
00:12:07,494 --> 00:12:13,285
Vokzal oldidagi supermarketga boramizmi?

183
00:12:13,308 --> 00:12:20,941
Ha, u yerda sabzavotlar ham arzon.

184
00:12:20,964 --> 00:12:28,031
Doʻkonda juda sovuq ekan, shundaymi?

185
00:12:28,055 --> 00:12:37,653
Ha, konditsioner juda kuchli.

186
00:12:37,677 --> 00:12:41,667
Goʻsht qayerda?

187
00:12:41,691 --> 00:12:50,524
Ana u yerda. Baliqning yonida.

188
00:12:50,547 --> 00:12:57,532
Choʻchqa goʻshti va mol goʻshti, qaysi birini yaxshi koʻrasiz?

189
00:12:57,555 --> 00:13:05,904
Ikkalasini ham yaxshi koʻraman, lekin bugun choʻchqa goʻshtini olamiz.

190
00:13:05,928 --> 00:13:14,161
Tushunarli. Bu choʻchqa goʻshti qanday?

191
00:13:14,184 --> 00:13:24,417
300 yen ekan. Arzon, shu olamiz.

192
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:29,632
Qanday sabzavotlar olamiz?

193
00:13:29,656 --> 00:13:36,289
Karam va piyoz olamiz.

194
00:13:36,312 --> 00:13:42,579
Shuningdek, tuxum ham kerak.

195
00:13:42,602 --> 00:13:51,270
Tuxum muzlatgichda hali bor.

196
00:13:51,293 --> 00:13:57,806
Shundaymi? Unda, faqat shular yetarli.

197
00:13:57,830 --> 00:14:04,339
Ha, kassaga boramiz.

198
00:14:04,362 --> 00:14:12,396
Pulni men toʻlayman.

199
00:14:12,419 --> 00:14:15,419
8-Sahna: Ovqatlanish suhbati

200
00:14:15,419 --> 00:14:19,393
Ovqat tayyor! Kelib yeying.

201
00:14:19,417 --> 00:14:23,983
Vov, qanday yaxshi hid kelmoqda!

202
00:14:24,006 --> 00:14:30,513
Bugun choʻchqa goʻshti va sabzavot qovurilgan.

203
00:14:30,537 --> 00:14:33,670
Juda mazali koʻrinadi.

204
00:14:33,693 --> 00:14:36,165
Yeyishni boshlayman.

205
00:14:36,188 --> 00:14:38,766
Yeyishni boshlayman.

206
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:42,256
Taʼmi qanday?

207
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:46,146
Juda mazali!

208
00:14:46,169 --> 00:14:49,738
Biroz achchiq ekan.

209
00:14:49,762 --> 00:14:52,595
Kechirasiz.

210
00:14:52,618 --> 00:14:57,285
Men achchiq taomlarni yaxshi koʻraman.

211
00:14:57,308 --> 00:15:00,226
Muammo yoʻq.

212
00:15:00,249 --> 00:15:04,149
Men ham achchiq narsalarni yaxshi koʻraman.

213
00:15:04,172 --> 00:15:07,715
Choy ichasizmi?

214
00:15:07,739 --> 00:15:11,209
Ha, iltimos.

215
00:15:11,232 --> 00:15:15,466
Bugungi yarim kunlik ish qanday boʻldi?

216
00:15:15,489 --> 00:15:20,756
Band edi, lekin qiziqarli boʻldi.

217
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:23,939
Bu yaxshi yangilik.

218
00:15:23,963 --> 00:15:27,063
Charchadingizmi?

219
00:15:27,086 --> 00:15:32,224
Ha, oyoqlarim biroz ogʻriyapti.

220
00:15:32,247 --> 00:15:37,349
Hammomga kirib, yaxshi dam oling.

221
00:15:37,372 --> 00:15:40,839
Ha, shunday qilaman.

222
00:15:40,862 --> 00:15:46,046
Bu taom haqiqatan ham mazali ekan, shunday emasmi?

223
00:15:46,069 --> 00:15:49,136
Rahmat.

224
00:15:49,159 --> 00:15:52,533
Yanaroq yeysizmi?

225
00:15:52,556 --> 00:15:57,089
Ha, iltimos, ozroq bering.

226
00:15:57,112 --> 00:16:02,882
Koʻp bor, hammasini yeb qoʻying.

227
00:16:02,906 --> 00:16:08,246
Ha, mazali ekan, hammasini yeyman.

228
00:16:08,269 --> 00:16:11,269
Sahna 9: Kundalik suhbatlar va sevimli mashgʻulotlar

229
00:16:11,269 --> 00:16:15,369
Televizorni yoqsam boʻladi-mi?

230
00:16:15,392 --> 00:16:18,950
Ha, iltimos.

231
00:16:18,974 --> 00:16:23,768
Qiziqarli biror koʻrsatuv bormi?

232
00:16:23,791 --> 00:16:29,258
Hozir sevimli animem boshlanadi.

233
00:16:29,282 --> 00:16:32,191
Qanday anime?

234
00:16:32,214 --> 00:16:37,914
Maktab oʻquvchilari sport bilan shugʻullanadigan anime.

235
00:16:37,937 --> 00:16:42,614
Vay, qiziqarli koʻrinadi.

236
00:16:42,637 --> 00:16:46,137
Men ham koʻrmoqchiman.

237
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:50,193
Bu juda mashhur anime.

238
00:16:50,216 --> 00:16:54,283
Bu qoʻshiq juda yaxshi ekan.

239
00:16:54,306 --> 00:16:57,373
Kimning qoʻshigʻi?

240
00:16:57,396 --> 00:17:01,989
Mashhur bir guruhning qoʻshigʻi.

241
00:17:02,012 --> 00:17:04,845
Koʻp tinglaysizmi?

242
00:17:04,868 --> 00:17:11,168
Ha, baʼzan internetda tinglayman.

243
00:17:11,191 --> 00:17:15,334
Men esa har kuni tinglayman.

244
00:17:15,358 --> 00:17:20,425
Anime qahramonlari koʻp ekan-ku.

245
00:17:20,448 --> 00:17:27,481
Ha, men uzun sochli shu yigitni yaxshi koʻraman.

246
00:17:27,504 --> 00:17:30,538
Juda chiroyli ekan.

247
00:17:30,561 --> 00:17:34,194
U kuchli-mi?

248
00:17:34,217 --> 00:17:40,057
Ha, eng kuchlisi va mehribon.

249
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:43,947
Syujetni bilish qiziq.

250
00:17:43,970 --> 00:17:50,070
Har juma oqshomlari efirga uzatiladi.

251
00:17:50,093 --> 00:17:54,526
Keyin kelasi hafta ham birga koʻraylik.

252
00:17:54,549 --> 00:17:58,095
Ha, shunday qilamiz.

253
00:17:58,118 --> 00:18:02,356
Shirinlik yeb, koʻraylikmi?

254
00:18:02,379 --> 00:18:05,716
Men olib kelaman.

255
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:08,740
Sahna 10: Dam olish va yarim kunlik ish haqida suhbat

256
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:13,730
Kecha yarim tunda oʻn bir yarim ekan-ku.

257
00:18:13,753 --> 00:18:18,427
Ha, endi uxlash vaqti.

258
00:18:18,451 --> 00:18:22,685
Ertaga soat nechada turasiz?

259
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:28,275
Ertaga dam olish kunim, sekin turaman.

260
00:18:28,298 --> 00:18:31,238
Yaxshi boʻlardi.

261
00:18:31,261 --> 00:18:35,830
Men esa ertaga ham yarim kunlik ishlayman.

262
00:18:35,854 --> 00:18:37,891
E?

263
00:18:37,914 --> 00:18:41,687
Yakshanba kunlari ham ishlaysizmi?

264
00:18:41,711 --> 00:18:46,211
Ha, ertalab soat toʻqqizdan boshlayman.

265
00:18:46,234 --> 00:18:49,615
Bu anchagina qiyin ekan.

266
00:18:49,639 --> 00:18:53,226
Necha soatda tugatasiz?

267
00:18:53,249 --> 00:18:57,034
Tushlik paytida soat ikkida tugataman.

268
00:18:57,058 --> 00:19:02,091
Unda tushdan keyin vaqt bor ekan.

269
00:19:02,114 --> 00:19:08,181
Ha. Tushdan keyin tozalash va kir yuvishni rejalashtirganman.

270
00:19:08,203 --> 00:19:12,637
Xonani tozalashda yordam beraman.

271
00:19:12,660 --> 00:19:15,371
Rostdanmi?

272
00:19:15,395 --> 00:19:18,153
Rahmat.

273
00:19:18,176 --> 00:19:23,743
Ha, siz doimo ovqat pishirib berasiz-ku.

274
00:19:23,766 --> 00:19:26,315
Katta yordam bo'ldi.

275
00:19:26,338 --> 00:19:31,910
Unda ertaga soat uchdan boshlab birga tozalaymiz.

276
00:19:31,933 --> 00:19:34,666
Tushunarli.

277
00:19:34,689 --> 00:19:39,356
Bugungi ob-havo maʼlumotini koʻrdingizmi?

278
00:19:39,379 --> 00:19:45,515
Ha, ertaga ob-havo juda yaxshi boʻladi, deyishgan.

279
00:19:45,538 --> 00:19:49,679
Kirlar yaxshi quriyapti, shundaymi?

280
00:19:49,703 --> 00:19:52,136
Ha, shunday.

281
00:19:52,159 --> 00:19:55,992
Endi chiroqni oʻchiraman.

282
00:19:56,015 --> 00:19:59,954
Xop. Yaxshi tun.

283
00:19:59,978 --> 00:20:02,617
Yaxshi tun.

284
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:05,340
Ertaga koʻrishamiz.